data.description: It's like you're always on vacation when you own this home on private "Little Lake Lasalle" After a hard day of work you can relax on the patio or in the grass and take in the beautiful lake view or take out your boat that waits for you by the dock right in your backyard!  This adorable spacious ranch has plenty of room with 4 bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms. The large eat in kitchen adjoins the cozy family room and both overlook the lake so you have lots of natural light during the day and the breeze off the lake in the evenings. The kitchen (updated 2014) is bright & spacious w/room for a large dining set. Plenty of counter space for meal prep and seating for bar chairs. All SS appliances & garbage disposal are included. The family room is the perfect place for indoors relaxing and allows for a large entertainment wall & comfy sofas. The living room is also very spacious for entertaining during the upcoming holidays or just for everyday living. The large primary bedroom is decorated in popular colors and has a large walk-in closet, wood laminate flooring and a full, private, modern bathroom attached with newer flooring & lighting. The other 3 bedrooms are all good sized and with popular color theme and newer carpeting. There's really not much for you to do but make this home your own! See the following information regarding updates. 2022-new sump pump; 2021- vinyl siding, sliding door, outdoor lighting, new carpet for 3 bedrooms, master bath flooring and lighting, fresh paint, landscape rock, garbage disposal; 2020-windows; 2019-gutters and garage door replaced; 2016- brick patio and HVAC; 2014-Kitchen cabinets/lighting; kitchen applicances, tile flooring in kitchen, dining, and laundry room, wood floor in living room and hallway; 2013-roof.
